ER24 paramedics arriving on the scene found a woman “sitting on the pavement”, ER24 spokeswoman Ineke van Huyssteen said. She sustained moderate injuries and was transported to hospital by ER24.
“A man sustained serious injuries and was transported to hospital by another medical service on the scene. It is believed that the man, unfortunately, succumbed to his injuries shortly after arriving at the hospital.”
The cause of the crash was not yet known, she said.
– African News Agency (ANA)